==Dutch==
===Verb===
'''aangeven'''
{{nl-verb-irreg|geef aan|geeft aan|gaf aan|aangegeven|aangevend}}
# To [[hand]], to [[pass]]: {''kun je me de afstandsbediening aangeven?'' --- can you hand me the remote control?}.
# To [[indicate]], to make [[clear]]: {''hij heeft aangegeven waar het is'' --- he has indicated where it is (to be found)}.
# To [[report]], to [[notify]]: {''iemand aangeven'' --- to report someone (to the authorities)}.
# To [[declare]]: {''niets aan te geven'' --- nothing to declare}.

